title: Test Driver (1940 Film-Noir) Directed by Christy Cabanne - Starring Richard Arlen

sources.title: Test Driver (1940 Film-Noir) Directed by Christy Cabanne - Starring Richard Arlen
sources.description:
Danger on Wheels is a 1940 American film noir sport film directed by Christy Cabanne and starring Richard Arlen and Andy Devine.

Synopsis: A test driver (Richard Arlen) tries racing with his girlfriend's (Peggy Moran) father's new engine.


Colorized version https://youtu.be/UTgmi4EniMU

Director: Christy Cabanne
Writers: Ben Pivar, Maurice Tombragel
Stars: Richard Arlen, Andy Devine, Peggy Moran
Genres: Noir, Sport, Thriller
Release date: February 2, 1940 (USA)
